{"tid":664191,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[胡迪]王思佳走光怒喊告　老公以「胸貼」相挺","createTime":"2018-05-14T01:09:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T13:36:59.000Z","uid":66943,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c9294c1036c5f5a6955cf96ac463a7a051b9beb7","tid":664191,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T01:09:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N6ndGR-o670\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DN6ndGR-o670&d=DUh6sihs39eOmPFGCy%2Fo54zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=a4a0decd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N6ndGR-o670</a><br />\n<br />\n王思佳喊告。（圖／翻攝自臉書 , 2018.5.13）<br />\n藝人王思佳近日參加活動，不慎走光，被媒體大肆報導後，12日晚間在臉書喊告，「正在整理截圖資料凖備報案。」對於愛妻不慎走光，王思佳老公Joe留言「Love you」力挺，還附上胸貼合照，以行動支持老婆。<br />\n<br />\n王思佳在臉書寫下，「發生了沒有人願意發生的事，謝謝很多暖心的留言和私信，相較於見死不救的現場媒體，世界上還是有同理心的朋友，一整天感謝大家熱心的資訊，正在整理截圖資料凖備報案，拿我尋開心傷口撒鹽瘋傳的，我面對我該面對的風風雨雨，接下來換你們面對法律責任。」她強調，「伸出援手的我一輩子會記得，落井下石的我會活的比你長。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n痴線只許露點炒作 不許百姓轉載<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/12/154756_0b1ef2ca009e84c817804495e5e7e8f9.png?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F12%2F154756_0b1ef2ca009e84c817804495e5e7e8f9.png%3F&d=DUh6sihs39eOmPFGCy%2Fo54zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=51dfa4c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/12/154756_0b1ef2ca009e84c817804495e5e7e8f9.png?</a>"},{"pid":"3b011761cefe59f2ed5dc6d004797e0a8339d817","tid":664191,"uid":13638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T01:32:40.000Z","msg":"告咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3c27111c7253ce7b9a51e5ef2b75fc412e8e2e4","tid":664191,"uid":90644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b011761cefe59f2ed5dc6d004797e0a8339d817","tid":664191,"uid":13638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"rep